channel.title: Price Checker/Trade Offers [Zybez API]
channel.description:
I made this when I was bored over the past 12 or so hours. It's an application that uses the zybez price guide api and sorts the data.
Download: http://www.mediafire.com/download/riv9jij80n9nl1g/07_Exchange.jar
Source (without libraries): http://www.mediafire.com/download/7o5vcpw2gh67g0p/org.rar
I'll be working on restoring images but for the time being they've been removed. They caused a horrendous amount of lag when inserted and rendered in a JTable, I'll try to fix that though.
Let me know if you find any bugs or have any suggestions.
